Product name: Antique Art Deco Bridal Hair Clip, OOAK Small 1920s Rhinestone Flapper Hair Accessory, 1930 Vintage Gatsby Hair Comb, Edwardian Victorian
Description:
Offering a stunning unique smaller scale Art Deco/Edwardian bridal hair clip made from an authentic 1920's - 1930's era paste rhinestone dress/fur clip.  An ornate, very well made, 2 1/8 inch (5.3 cm) long by 1 1/8 inch (2.8 cm) wide pot metal SO Art Deco/Edwardian shaped setting is completely encrusted in varying sized sparkly clear round cut crystals and has been securely attached to a new high quality silver plated alligator clip base.  I love the simple yet elegant shape and design of this one and the way the designer set the crystals so close together!  It's smaller but it has SO much presence!  Jewel is in wonderful vintage condition with all rhinestones present, accounted for, and bright.  Though it has so much sparkle, the jewel has mellowed just a tad creating that softer authentic antique look and feel that can only be achieved with age.  They don't make jewelry anymore with this quality. Don't settle for vintage "look" (that always looks like a reproduction) cookie-cutter produced when you can have a unique hair comb made from a true antique/vintage jewel!  (Note last photos is of Downton Abbey's Lady Mary just to give you a better idea of how the comb could be used.  It would also be lovely clipped next to an updo).
 Clip will arrive wrapped in tissue inside a gift box.
*** Regarding quality - I have been making altered couture jewelry from vintage jewels for years. I use high quality silver and gold plated comb and clip bases and guarantee that the jewels will not come off. If you read through my feedback, you will find that my clients continue to be very happy with the quality of the pieces they purchase from my shop as well as the outstanding customer service.
